content: अज् {c1c} <ab>P.</ab> (optionally replaced by the root वी in non-conjugational tenses; अजति, आजीत्, अजितुं) {@--1@} To go. {@--2@} To drive, lead. {@--3@} To throw, cast (used with prepositions found only in Vedic literature).
